---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Ajmal Khan writes TestEnigma &#8212; testing software with AI, and testing AI itself."
  active="about"
>
  <div class="wrap about-wrap">
    <img class="avatar-lg" src="/images/profile.jpg" alt="Ajmal Khan" style="object-fit:cover" />
    <div class="about-body">
      <div class="eyebrow">About</div>
      <h1>Hi, I&#8217;m Ajmal Khan</h1>
      <p>Add a short bio here &#8212; who you are, what you work on day to day, and what TestEnigma is about.</p>
      <p>A second paragraph works well for the specifics: the kind of problems you dig into, the tools you use, or what you&#8217;re currently exploring at the intersection of testing and AI.</p>
      <p>Have feedback, a correction, or an idea for a post? Reach out on LinkedIn, or leave a comment on any post here.</p>
      <div class="pill-row">
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ajmal-khan-98254871/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
